## Limitations

This report is based on data available up to October 2023 and may not capture the most recent developments related to the pandemic. Additionally, the findings are drawn from a limited number of sources, which may not represent the full spectrum of changes experienced globally. Further research is needed to explore long-term impacts and regional variations in pandemic responses.

